Revision history for perl module Input::Validator

0.001005 2012-02-13

 - Do not clear other messages when calling messages method on a field
   (reported by Marcus Ramberg)

0.001004 2011-07-05

 - Do not keep wrong values, there is a separate method "all_values" now

0.001003 2011-07-05

 - Fixed callback custom error setting
 - Keep wrong field's value
 - Set custom error messages per field

0.001002 2011-05-26

 - Fixed conditions inflate bug (found by Alex Voronov)

0.001001 2011-05-05

 - Initial release
